                "imgDesc": "<p>Certain skills and effects can grant characters wielding Swords, Claymores, and Polearms with an <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">Elemental Infusion</span>: Normal, Charged, and Plunging Attacks will deal Elemental DMG of the corresponding element. The effects of multiple Infusions do not stack.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/2"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/10/21/25750596/0a506e3b6069f95df94aee0e5f88a706_7442130916836101351.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>Additionally, some skills can convert character's attacks, making them deal Elemental DMG. Even though this effect is similar to Infusion, it <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">cannot be overridden by any Elemental Infusion</span>.</p>",
